<P>
 Amgen Inc., Amcell Corp. Announce Collaboration: The companies said they have 
agreed to develop and commercialize products based on proprietary cell 
separation and characterization technology developed in Germany.The agreement 
gives Amgen, the Thousand Oaks-based biotechnology giant, exclusive worldwide 
