<DOCID> 021814 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 11, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 5; Column 1; View Desk 
